---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Founder — Nous Ergon"
  description="Brian McMahon founded Nous Ergon, an applied AI lab, in March 2026 — bringing together careers in finance and in data and AI engineering."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Brian McMahon</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-8">Founder</p>

    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Brian founded Nous Ergon in March 2026 to build agentic systems against
      problems with measurable, continuously verifiable outcomes. The lab
      brings together his two careers: finance first, then data and AI
      engineering.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      He began in finance &mdash; a CPA at Deloitte, middle-market investment
      banking in San Francisco, then investment advisory in Asia &mdash; with
      an MBA in Finance from CEIBS and London Business School. He then moved
      into data science: an MS in Computer Science (machine learning) from
      Georgia Tech and eight years of data engineering and machine learning
      in fintech and healthcare, most recently at Block. The full background
      is on
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brian-c-mcmahon/">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      The lab's work is public and running:
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://crucible.nousergon.ai/">Crucible</a>
      publishes its results to a
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://live.nousergon.ai/">live dashboard</a>,
      and the
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://dev.nousergon.ai/">developer tools</a>
      are open source on
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://github.com/nousergon">GitHub</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">Links</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brian-c-mcmahon/">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://github.com/cipher813">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="mailto:brian@nousergon.ai">brian@nousergon.ai</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>
